Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:56.52,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}照れくさいほど近づいて　聞こえたい聲がある
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.43,0:01:03.62,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ワガママ-ムリ-言いたい放題　聞かせてよアイの正體
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.61,0:01:10.89,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}むずかしいから逃げちゃった　悲しくて前を見て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:18.38,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}再び發つ大地呼んで　汗握るおおきな滿月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:25.42,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}格好イイと格好ワルイ　どうして極端なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.49,0:01:35.03,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大スキで大っキライな事しかわからないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.10,0:01:36.54,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}始まった？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.60,0:01:39.93,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}LANDS STAR　一種の冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.94,0:01:43.70,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ひとりじゃないって手を繫ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:47.01,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}MIGHT STAR　目を閉じて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:51.10,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}わたしともっと息を吸って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:02:00.98,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ミライがキレイな方へと動くように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:56.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}靠近到害羞的距離  為的是聽到那個聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.43,0:01:03.62,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}任性地自說自話  讓我領教一下愛的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.61,0:01:10.89,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}面對困難選擇逃避  悲傷地看向前方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:18.38,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}再次起身召喚大地  滿月也捏了一把汗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:25.42,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}帥和衰  為什麼只有兩個極端
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.49,0:01:35.03,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}要不是喜歡就是討厭  我只知道這兩者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.10,0:01:36.54,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}開始了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.60,0:01:39.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}LANDS STAR  一場冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.94,0:01:43.70,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你不是一個人  牽起手來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:47.01,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}MIGHT STAR  閉上雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:51.10,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}和我一起接受更多的空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:02:00.98,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}願未來向更美好的方向發展
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:09.89,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}身近にいてもよく知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.29,0:22:17.47,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ため息　心配を乘せて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:25.42,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この街を拔ける　明日を想う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.80,0:22:28.33,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}なにか言ってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.44,0:22:32.11,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}なにか…おねがい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.55,0:22:39.34,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「夢を見たけど憶えてないの」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.45,0:22:45.90,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れたふりが下手だと教えないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:52.37,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}まっすぐなキモチが前を見てる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.37,0:22:55.70,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}喜びを見てる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:23:01.11,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}迷い消して　Ride on  Ride on RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.18,0:23:06.66,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}まっすぐに風がえがく回掃線
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:08.63,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}氣がついたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:19.99,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Ah  ときめき眠る前に早く…早く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:09.89,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即便在身邊  也不是什麼都明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.29,0:22:17.47,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}嘆息中蘊含著心里的擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:25.42,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心想著離開這座城市的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.80,0:22:28.33,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}真心希望你能說些話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.44,0:22:32.11,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}真心希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.55,0:22:39.34,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「雖然做了一個夢  但卻不記得了」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.45,0:22:45.90,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}請別和我說  我不擅長假裝忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:52.37,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}率直的感情面向著前方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.37,0:22:55.70,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}面向著喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:23:01.11,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}消除心中的迷茫  Ride on  Ride on RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.18,0:23:06.66,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}率直的風描繪著回歸線
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:08.63,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一旦注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:19.99,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就在心動不已的感覺消失前  趕緊行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:16.52,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ざわめく街の外へ誘われた偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:23.85,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}なぜでしょう　迴り會えたこのときめき
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:31.14,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ただ待ってるようじゃいけない…わかりました！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.41,0:18:41.96,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}目の前に開いたセカイの旅を　さあ始めるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:48.41,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}願いを乘せて吹く　色とりどりの風模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.41,0:18:50.26,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}もっとキレイに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:54.53,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}かわる魔法はどこ？　あのひとはどこ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:57.81,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}聲がふるえても
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:19:04.77,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}キセキを信じて進みますわ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:16.52,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}在喧鬧的鎮外  碰到意想不到的緣分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:23.85,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}為什麼呢  這邂逅使得心跳如此加速
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:31.14,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}僅僅等待是不行的…我明白了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.41,0:18:41.96,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}就在眼前世界之旅  馬上啟程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:48.41,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}寄託著我的心願  五彩繽紛的風兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.41,0:18:50.26,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}變得更加漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:54.53,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}哪里有變身魔法？  那個人又在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:57.81,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}儘管聲音已經顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:19:04.77,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}依然堅信著奇跡  邁出那一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.35,0:00:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉娜  有客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.48,0:00:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:14.11,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,270)\fad(1000,0)}羈絆之杖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:14.11,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,270)\fad(1000,0)}羈絆之杖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然蛋糕還是水果蛋糕最好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尼艾絲你昨天還說芝士蛋糕好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天就果餡餅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探戈也來一口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  阿尼艾絲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  卡莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.52,0:02:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換我的蛋糕給你好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在看她的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是在看什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.39,0:02:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.66,0:02:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要製造像探戈那樣能說話的自動人偶很困難吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  能以自己的意志和心靈來對話的自動人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實需要特殊的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.51,0:03:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在聊什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下午還有公務  就先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是夠忙的啊  不過畢竟她是大公之女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能幹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尼艾絲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  卡莉娜小姐她在想這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.49,0:03:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有什麼能幫得到她的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:04:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.92,0:04:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？雷斯塔和阿尼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  他們呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還真不愧是雷斯塔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就看晶石怪物了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉娜小姐  歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  卡莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔  阿尼  你們倆有商量什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？算是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  卡莉娜小姐  我有個想接受的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是拉修塔特森林和在那里盛開的黑虹花的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑虹花？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說彩虹還看得出來  黑是指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:05:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}原本是黑色的花  據說是吸收了周圍的光芒就變成了七色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真是稀奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因此在森林中花開之地的四周尤其陰暗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  就跟晶石吸收艾爾一般  花在吸收光芒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林本來就已經很陰暗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加之在黑暗之中還有被晶石怪物襲擊的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是難度非常高的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過因此也比較容易找到好的晶石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}嗯  而且Oasis也多了阿尼艾絲和切露西這樣的強力夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得現在應該可以做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  卡莉娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就接受這個任務吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特是第一次乘坐列車嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  好激動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  米內特這樣很危險哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.41,0:06:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能把身子伸出列車的窗外哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很好  摸摸頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.78,0:06:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個傢伙看起來真像好姐妹一般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  那黑虹花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林這麼廣闊  你打算怎麼找啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉娜  我覺得應該先從上空偵察
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  卡莉娜小姐可以用魔法飛起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就由我們從上空偵察  找到周圍陰暗的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  由阿尼艾絲她們到那地點去把花回收
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶石怪物出現的話  就輪到我們上場了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸運啊  因為搬運貨物的任務碰巧到車站來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能遇到雷斯塔他們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  感覺要碰上寶貝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:18.67,pos2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(465,20)\fad(200,0)}（易碎物）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:18.67,pos2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,260)\fad(200,0)\c000000}（易碎物）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真對不起啊  把你塞進這麼窄的貨物室里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼差不多該到客室上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我忘了告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為太急  所以客室的票只買到這一張而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了這麼重要的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  姐姐你有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:44.92,pos2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,25)\c000000}（鮮活產品）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:48.93,pos2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(174,25)\c000000}（鮮活產品）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:48.95,pos2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(382,25)\c000000}（易碎物）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我也要當貨物嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  飛起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉娜  已經完全跟蒙緹基亞一心同體了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為是雷斯塔給我做的珍貴的杖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你  卡莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給我？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是給卡莉娜做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體弱的我能到外面暢遊都是多虧了這蒙緹基亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能聽你這麼說我也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:09:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你跟阿尼說些什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉娜  那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計是黑虹花  聯繫大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  向北走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  北邊是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走到河邊就往左走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北是上邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以這草為標記…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣沿著懸崖邊直走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  這還真是美景啊切露
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切露？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.87,0:09:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？咦？啊  切露！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左邊？  右邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉娜小姐  停下停下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看懸崖對面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切露？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們先走  我去接切露然後追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是上邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔他們的目的地似乎是從這里一直往北的那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  格雷姆  全速前進
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方可是無底沼澤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以讓你把重要的東西早點說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真苦了你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.14,0:10:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是  黑虹花…好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.71,0:11:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶石怪物這麼快就出現了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別離開我  卡莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲在黑暗中攻擊我們嗎  真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用光魔法來照亮黑暗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  光會被黑虹花吸收掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在擋下下一次攻擊時  我會把怪物頂到那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.61,0:11:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後你用魔法攻破那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得到嗎  卡莉娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:11:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:11:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.93,0:12:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  怪物哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太專注沒把魔力的力道控制好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上去拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷斯塔  請不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被藤蔓纏住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能看  米內特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這不是什麼見不得人的事…這個  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.39,0:13:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認完畢  任務完成  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.11,0:13:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後多注意點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉娜也沒事了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們受驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是倒楣啊  竟然在最後關頭魔力耗盡掉了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒臉見人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  既然完成了任務就都算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還意外獲得了這麼好的晶石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事啊…各位  能把這晶石交給我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  阿尼艾絲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼好的晶石用來改良蒙緹基亞是最好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在想用這個晶石或許可以讓蒙緹基亞附上會話機能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙緹基亞會變得能說話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實昨天雷斯塔就跟我商量了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:15:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}蒙緹基亞能說話的話  像今天這樣魔力耗盡前就會提醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還可以跟你談心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  卡莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了  我給你沖了杯紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  卡莉娜  能幫我一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:16:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我完全不懂  幫忙的話找阿尼不是更好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽阿尼艾絲說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}最起碼要有優質的晶石和專業技術  不過最重要的是羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.05,0:16:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羈絆嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個探戈也是  它是我小時候生日收到的布偶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人所愛  所重視的東西會有靈魂寄宿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師父是這麼對我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羈絆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.44,0:16:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  卡莉娜重視蒙緹基亞的心才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要怎麼做才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟平常一樣向蒙緹基亞注入魔力看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來控制艾爾的流向
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不  我覺得很香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  因為我剛剛洗完澡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣了吧  按理說應該沒錯了的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莉娜  試著啟動一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是艾爾的流轉不順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再重頭來過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就再去沖杯紅茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里  這點小事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是這樣還不行的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼讓您受驚了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  成功了啊卡莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  蒙緹基亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}情況已把握  您是在為我擁有意識懂得對話這個事實驚訝的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  雖然事先知道  但還是吃了一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.03,0:19:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙緹基亞  有什麼不適應的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認狀態  與改良前比較  現狀沒有任何問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臆測情報  我的意識中早就有著想為主人們效勞的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補充說明  是指我的製造者雷斯塔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛護我的主人  和Oasis的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:20:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  雖然之前不能說話  但一直是這麼想的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.69,0:20:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後也請多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常榮幸  請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是太高興了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明事項
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊  蒙緹？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚兩位的氣氛非常融洽  不過相讓而過是故意的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？你在說什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨夜就如主人所願  雷斯塔先生對主人起了慾望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慾望…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳數和體溫都上升  中途想起了些什麼又停下手來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這個…也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提示疑問  有什麼好害羞的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人每天晚上都向雷斯塔先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哇  不准說不准說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.22,0:20:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的聲音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來很成功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求說明  為了今後能幫上主人的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請一定要給我說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃不下了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}喂  姐姐  現在可不是說這些老套夢話的時候  天亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.25,0:21:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回埃爾塔利亞去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走  格雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等等啊莉特絲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丟下我…餵你先把衣服給我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:21:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來抓我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺像大家一起來郊遊了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.12,0:23:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謎之光？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.16,0:23:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西是上等貨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.94,0:23:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再地震的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.89,0:23:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米內特  危險
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.02,0:23:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳得好厲害
